Short Description:
Ocean Transworld Logistics Pvt. Ltd. (OTWL) is a logistics and freight forwarding company based in Mumbai. The company specializes in technology-driven supply chain solutions, offering services in air, sea, and land freight, customs clearance, warehousing, and distribution. OTWL utilizes AI-powered platforms to provide end-to-end transparency and real-time tracking, ensuring efficient and secure operations.

OTWL's service offerings include comprehensive freight forwarding solutions, customs clearance for import and export, and warehousing with inventory tracking. The company also provides transportation and distribution services, handling everything from first-mile to last-mile delivery. Additionally, OTWL is equipped to manage project cargo and specialized logistics for oversized or time-sensitive items. Their digital approach simplifies complex logistics, making it easier for clients to navigate their supply chain needs.
